  <metadata>
    <name>VIE-L3 — Semmering &amp; Southern Alps Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from VIE and ride into the Semmering &amp; Southern Alps. Hit Wiener Neustadt and Semmering Pass — 985m. Loop back to VIE over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
